{"tid":830784,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★ 43%僱員八號波黑雨返工 多不獲交通津貼 惡劣天氣遲到要扣薪","createTime":"2018-09-21T11:47:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-22T09:39:19.000Z","uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b4b1c73fbcd080ae4f324210e60c9ee0a72f4aaa","tid":830784,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T11:47:13.000Z","msg":"強颱風山竹襲港期間，不少打工仔要冒險上班。港九勞工社團聯會昨發表調查，六百零七名受訪者中，四成三需於八號或以上熱帶氣旋警告信號或黑雨警告生效期間上班，當中以保安、飲食及醫療等行業最常見；五成四在沒有任何安排下冒險上班，僅不足兩成四獲僱主安排交通或有交通津貼。另有合共兩成八受訪打工仔指，若因惡劣天氣而遲到或缺勤，會被扣工資或勤工獎，疑違反勞工處相關守則。有僱主更疑在知道颱風將至後，預先安排員工在打風日放假<br />\n<br />\n調查於今年三月至五月進行，結果發現，保安及物業管理、旅遊、飲食及酒店業、運輸及醫療等行業僱員，最常需要在颱風期間上班。多達七成六受訪者指，打風期間上班不獲安排膳食，六成半指僱主不會發放當值津貼。<br />\n<br />\n被問到若因惡劣天氣而遲到或缺勤，兩成稱會被扣工資或影響勤工獎表現；近一成更指會同時被扣工資及影響勤工獎。另有三成二受訪者指，僱主在知悉颱風將至後，刻意安排員工在八號或以上信號懸掛期間放年假、法定假期或休息日，明顯違反《僱傭條例》，僱主不應扣減僱員假期的規定，屬違法行為。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20180921/00176_012.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180921%2F00176_012.html&d=X2mAhVlg6XDRO7%2FRs9GaQQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=2604543e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20180921/00176_012.html</a>"},{"pid":"b023cea8c7e658d41cd2a66001f907aa3bcb0725","tid":830784,"uid":65530,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T11:47:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"49ffe881fca645093254f9f345993dfda0ada067","tid":830784,"uid":19454,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T11:47:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/17/112648_485fc3d2d1d7936bbfd233b1b1d6df46.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F17%2F112648_485fc3d2d1d7936bbfd233b1b1d6df46.png&h=9c9f5cff&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d2d2a4c41b036323f8671189235b4ff5a2098c56","tid":830784,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T11:50:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/17/130744_caa6a4dd0f72c869ebf0ba5a41d667f7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F17%2F130744_caa6a4dd0f72c869ebf0ba5a41d667f7.png&h=f29bef70&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6e0bd0944a3fc8e3fc5b900ecaea241bf154a2ef","tid":830784,"uid":151933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T11:53:25.000Z","msg":"多謝林鄭俾我番工<br />\n幾驚星期一唔駛番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c59fc163d91bd8f756f29a457ac9d37fc236df1","tid":830784,"uid":32952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T12:15:07.000Z","msg":"奴隸港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e1b28a453f4dab2b2d97a64eb3c002088ecc115","tid":830784,"uid":47080,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T12:23:59.000Z","msg":"林鄭下台！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6d334e129990fb4aad2d40c260663cf39a4850b","tid":830784,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T14:38:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a57a9aa339c62ac971bae228a9a283f7c44b9e3a","tid":830784,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T09:39:19.000Z","msg":"lm"}]}